  "title": "⚡🌟 SALES CONSULTANT - ENTRY LEVEL 🌟",
  "description": "<p>Training Provided | High Commission | Uncapped Earnings | Career Growth</p><p>📢 LOOKING FOR A SALES JOB WITH REAL GROWTH?</p><p>If you want:</p><p>To build skills that pay off</p><p>To earn based on your results, not just hours worked</p><p>A clear path for career progression</p><p>To join a supportive and driven team</p><p>This role is designed for people like YOU.</p><p>👥 WHO IS THIS ROLE FOR?</p><p>Fresh graduates ready to start strong</p><p>ORD personnel eager to build a future</p><p>Career switchers searching for a new direction</p><p>People with zero sales experience but high motivation</p><p>Attitude beats experience every time.</p><p>🔍 WHAT YOU WILL DO</p><p>Engage customers confidently and professionally</p><p>Learn to understand needs and present solutions</p><p>Handle objections and close sales with integrity</p><p>Work within a supportive, goal-oriented team</p><p>This is your chance to develop transferable communication and sales skills.</p><p>🎓 TRAINING & SUPPORT</p><p>Comprehensive onboarding program</p><p>Daily coaching from experienced mentors</p><p>Product knowledge and sales technique workshops</p><p>Consistent feedback and personal development</p><p>We invest in your growth because your success is our success.</p><p>💰 EARNINGS & INCENTIVES</p><p>Performance-based commission structure</p><p>Unlimited earning potential</p><p>Incentives and rewards for top performers</p><p>Opportunity to grow your income exponentially</p><p>🚀 CAREER PATH</p><p>Sales Consultant</p><p>Senior Sales Consultant</p><p>Team Leader</p><p>Manager</p><p>Promotion is based on your performance and leadership, not seniority.</p><p>🌍 TRAVEL & EXPERIENCES</p><p>Incentive trips for high achievers</p><p>Exposure to new markets</p><p>Opportunities for personal and professional growth beyond the usual desk job</p><p>🤝 TEAM & CULTURE</p><p>Motivated and supportive environment</p><p>Regular team-building activities and events</p><p>Recognition for hard work and achievements</p><p>Leaders who actively mentor and develop talent</p><p>❌ NOT FOR YOU IF</p><p>You want a guaranteed fixed salary without pressure</p><p>You avoid accountability</p><p>You dislike fast-paced, performance-driven environments</p><p>👉 READY TO TAKE THE NEXT STEP?</p><p>🔥 DM “CONSULT” or apply now</p><p>🔥 Limited slots for training available</p><p>This is your chance to build a rewarding career on your terms.</p>",
